TYPE LOCALITY. “in montosis Lybiae, Aegypti, Arabiae petreae” [= in the mountains of 
<collectingCountry box="[1141,1209,836,861]" name="Libya" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Libya</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1220,1289,836,860]" name="Egypt" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Egypt</collectingCountry>
, and 
